{
  "texts": [
    "45 2022 Luo Graph neural networks are utilized to synthesize node attributes and topological information.",
    "The extracted low-dimensional features are more representative, taking into account the nodes' own attributes and the relationships between nodes.",
    "47 2022 Luo A framework for predicting drug-target interactions by information aggregation based on heterogeneous graphical neural networks with incorporation of attention mechanisms.",
    "The method first obtains the molecular fingerprint information of the drug and the pseudo-amino acid composition information of the protein, and then extracts the initial features of the nodes by Bi-LSTM and aggregates the heterogeneous neighbors using the attention mechanism.",
    "Wang et al."
  ]
}